{"tid":961875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂 Switch 日本銷量超越 PS4 + PS4 Slim 總和","createTime":"2018-12-30T12:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T18:38:18.000Z","uid":105678,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bc0d6b990e503cbcc8f027ec826353795a53f9","tid":961875,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/nintendo-switch-1151759.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fnintendo-switch-1151759.jpeg&h=7f10bb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任天堂 Switch 推出以來，憑着創新的設計打破了之前 Wii U 的悶局，在家用遊戲機市場勢如破竹。最近有市場報告發現，Switch 在日本的銷量已經超越了 PS4 和 PS4 Slim 的總和。<br />\n<br />\n來自 Media Create 的市場報告指出，任天堂 Switch 在日本的銷量已經超過 667 萬部，除了超越了 PlayStation Vita 至今的總銷量之外，更是超過了 PlayStation 4 和 PlayStation 4 Slim 的銷量總和（654 萬部）。以 Switch 只是推出了不足兩年的時間看來，可以超越 PlayStation 4 和 Slim 累積 4 年的銷量實在不容易，以 PS4 Pro 的日本銷量約 100 萬部，Switch 要完全超前 PlayStation 4 系列也不無可能。<br />\n<br />\n至於在全球的表現 PlayStation 4 則仍然大幅拋離 Switch，前者銷量約 8,600 萬部，而 Switch 銷量則不足 2,000 萬。未來主機大戰會有怎樣的變化，仍然需要視乎有否吸引的大作帶動銷量，例如明年一月的 PS4 Biohazard 2 重製版以及 Switch 的 New Super Mario Bros. U Deluxe 都是令人期待的大作。<br />\n<br />\n來源：comicbook"},{"pid":"ba0e4f3541c7bd488e145aa44e794545d0dfb9c7","tid":961875,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"頭香"},{"pid":"060f83a385e52bd7a58318fc31ffea3cbd84b4c9","tid":961875,"uid":38316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"無嘢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2648981eb33c9c8f1d2ccb65a5e411581658288","tid":961875,"uid":126835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾任"},{"pid":"92306b729c658011f5dcd6ac75a0343cd0b2e525","tid":961875,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T12:39:58.00